{"tid":191532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[nba懷舊台] 只講得分邊個得分力最高","createTime":"2017-04-08T03:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T17:56:37.000Z","uid":70769,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58997789459164d75649b4611a383b3e18628cf","tid":191532,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/110411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F110411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5dcc6a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戰神最矮得分王，唔多介紹佢個名已經話左比你知- - - 答案<br />\n<br />\n暫時講下mj後curry前 nba pg，sg，sf 得分好手，一定有漏，搵d我仲記得ga人講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/110509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F110509_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=969e841a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT mac 身體天賦爆登，最深刻一定係干拔跳3分同打板入樽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/111347_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F111347_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c406051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nvc 半人半神，而為佢得入樽？其實又唔係三分，突破，中投全部都係頂級之上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/111508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F111508_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=54a12cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安東尼初入聯盟時同占士一時瑜亮，最多變攻擊手段，高低位進攻及背框面框手段樣樣皆精<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/111736_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F111736_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d227bf55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwade 閃電突破03 3子最先奪冠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/111908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F111908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c6934c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大將軍， agent zero 唔講道理超遠三分，顏射三分，包夾三分，半場三分，最癲時每場第4節一定著火，號篇要係全nba所有球隊上都要拎過60分以上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/112124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F112124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4f216445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLBJ king唔多介紹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/112143_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F112143_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=caa38b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冷門d或者比人睇底左ga ray gun，佢唔止得三分，突破都快狠準，同ai 由大學鬥到nba。有興趣遲下再開post講下<br />\n<br />\n最後有個人不在呢個post討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，講埋佢，呢個post一定收皮，我唔用文字話你知係邊個大家睇圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/112456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F112456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=151cfa18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cd9580de1f281d921475215d3e9b04288e053a6","tid":191532,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"T mac加高佬明嗰陣好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3935d2031a09c10d7530fb4c808fde6eeb66ac1","tid":191532,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"