:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"反而卡達傷完出來都仲keep到，成日覺得佢打得自私d係可以再拎高分d，印象中佢生涯好似未試過拎多過60分"},{"pid":"001240137eee51182ff4aae13aff84f206d7cc51","tid":191532,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"vc唔係Bowen條那渣閪既話 成就唔止而家咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然而家都好撚好j 40歲仲可以做到你張圖個入樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可想而知佢冇傷有幾撚癲<br />\nvc deserves a ring<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2269c6d875f1833e4887cedc5879f39061c591","tid":191532,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而卡達傷完出來都仲keep到，成日覺得佢打得自私d係可以再拎高分d，印象中佢生涯好似未試過拎多過60分</blockquote><br />\n５１分 佢既高分紀錄係有埋其他數據 唔係硬刷得分<br />\n印象最深係佢同kidd一齊攞大三元 係繼Jordan pippen之後同場兩個隊員同時攞triple double<br />\n佢果場好似攞48分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ab289177d7df19350228424d0dd192cbe11687","tid":191532,"uid":66767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"記得kobe唔知連續幾場50分<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabfe4336090f27b6698fe2c1fff79c9b97bd1b0","tid":191532,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"應該係高比<br />\n佢天生獨食架<br />\n<br />\nＴＭＡＣ就最後十幾秘先出招<br />\n<br />\nＣＡＲＴＥＲ　只識入樽。<br />\n<br />\nＡＩ　太矮，<br />\n<br />\nＲＡＹ　ＡＬＬＥＮ　只識射三分<br />\n<br />\n守佢三分線就攪掂"},{"pid":"0dd0ed077dfa382609787d88a45c55e084f4f757","tid":191532,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前pg黎講arenas得分能力算唔算top 3?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得佢好型</blockquote